Partners Hierarchy

Build parters hierarchy by specifying partner categories

Main Features:

  • Partners Menu
  • Partner Categories
  • Setting Category
  • Filter by Category

Partners Menu

A "Partners" menu added next to the "Users" menu in "Settings" makes convenient to access and manage partners.

Partner Categories

Define partner categories in with child-parent relations.

Setting Category

There are two ways of linking partners to categories - set one category on partner form or set many partners for one category on category form.

Filter by Category

A filtering and grouping by category is possible for parter views.

Quality Check

Module passed following quality control checks

The Odoo Community Association pylint-odoo

Module passed OCA standards by testing with OCA odoo-pylint tests.

More info: https://github.com/OCA/pylint-odoo.
